Column_8: Function description: During the navigation process of the robot, the corner point of the path is an important factor affecting the motion state. In order to obtain better wall-mounting performance, the robot will strictly reach the corner point and rotate in place and continue to drive. If you do not need to strictly follow the line or pay for money during driving, you can also skip the corner point and directly track the subsequent path near the corner point. The parameter of the switching mode is (strategy.yaml) movebase: shortcut_corner. In addition, in shortcut corner mode, when the distance from the corner sentence is less than the specified range, the system will slow down.
功能说明_en: Function description: During the navigation process of the robot, the corner point of the path is an important factor affecting the motion state. In order to obtain better wall-mounting performance, the robot will strictly reach the corner point and rotate in place and continue to drive. If you do not need to strictly follow the line or pay for money during driving, you can also skip the corner point and directly track the subsequent path near the corner point. The parameter of the switching mode is (strategy.yaml) movebase: shortcut_corner. In addition, in shortcut corner mode, when the distance from the corner sentence is less than the specified range, the system will slow down.

Column_8: Function description: First of all, make sure that the installation direction of the lower computer is correct, that is, when the front of the machine is raised, the imu pitch value is in the raised state. Turn on the detection strategy switch on the app: /strategy/chassis/imu/roll_alarm_enable No shutdown and restart is required. The alarm trigger threshold can be modified on the app /strategy/chassis/imu/roll_alarm_threshold The roll angle of the alarm trigger /strategy/chassis/imu/pitch_alarm_threshold The pitch angle of the alarm trigger is required to shut down and restart after modification.
功能说明_en: Function description: First of all, make sure that the installation direction of the lower computer is correct, that is, when the front of the machine is raised, the imu pitch value is in the raised state. Turn on the detection strategy switch on the app: /strategy/chassis/imu/roll_alarm_enable No shutdown and restart is required. The alarm trigger threshold can be modified on the app /strategy/chassis/imu/roll_alarm_threshold The roll angle of the alarm trigger /strategy/chassis/imu/pitch_alarm_threshold The pitch angle of the alarm trigger is required to shut down and restart after modification.

Column_5: 1. Adjust the original negative pressure data check part. When the negative pressure value is abnormal, it is necessary to continue to monitor the speed of the air suction motor in the vacuum cleaner task mode; 2. Negative pressure blockage detection and air suction motor speed detection are independent. Both data need to be continuously monitored in the vacuum cleaner mode, and both alarms must be issued when abnormal; 3. Alarm issuance and clearing part: a. Perceive the alarms of 10184 and 10185, and the checker converts them according to the advanced parameters /device/scrubber/enable_fnl_influence_task (default false) (false means H1 alarm, true means H4 alarm) b. Alarm clearing is also based on the 10184 and 10185 alarms;
Column_8: https://gaussian.yuque.com/od6ghz/no74yv/xgyzeu55lp2p56tb?singleDoc# 《S-滚刷在位检测》 关闭：任务自检时，不会检测尘盒、HEPA等是否在位； 打开：

参数释义_en: 1. Adjust the original negative pressure data check part. When the negative pressure value is abnormal, it is necessary to continue to monitor the speed of the air suction motor in the vacuum cleaner task mode; 2. Negative pressure blockage detection and air suction motor speed detection are independent. Both data need to be continuously monitored in the vacuum cleaner mode, and both alarms must be issued when abnormal; 3. Alarm issuance and clearing part: a. Perceive the alarms of 10184 and 10185, and the checker converts them according to the advanced parameters /device/scrubber/enable_fnl_influence_task (default false) (false means H1 alarm, true means H4 alarm) b. Alarm clearing is also based on the 10184 and 10185 alarms;
